    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>That $100 Risotto</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Michael A Gould letter deplores idea of charging $100 for a plate of risotto (May 17 article)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>It was with shock and disbelief that I read Terrance Brennan's attempt to justify charging $100 for risotto. I don't plan to buy a plate of rice for a sum that would feed a hungry family, and Picholine's patrons might consider donating that amount to a (tax deductible) charity instead.</p>
        <p>MICHAEL A. GOULD  New York</p>
      </block>
